Class Sorter

java.lang.Object
  com.psddev.dari.db.Record
      com.psddev.dari.db.Sorter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Recordable, HtmlObject, BeanInfo, Cloneable, Comparable<Record>
@Recordable.Embedded
public class Sorter
extends Record

Sorter used to prioritize items returned from a query.

Following operators are available:

  • "ascending"
  • "closest"
  • "descending"
  • "farthest"
  • "relevant"
